<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rubik+Dirt&family=Oswald:wght@400;600;700&display=swap');
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  html, body { width: 1200px; height: 630px; overflow: hidden; background: #080806; }

.canvas {
width: 1200px;
height: 630px;
background: #080806;
display: flex;
align-items: center;
position: relative;
overflow: hidden;
}

.bg-glow {
position: absolute;
inset: 0;
background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 60%, rgba(30,50,10,0.5) 0%, transparent 65%);
pointer-events: none;
}

/* LEFT - brand */
.left {
position: relative;
z-index: 10;
padding: 0 0 0 64px;
flex: 0 0 580px;
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
justify-content: center;
}

.alert-pill {
display: inline-flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 7px;
background: rgba(232,146,10,0.1);
border: 1px solid rgba(232,146,10,0.25);
border-radius: 2px;
padding: 5px 12px;
margin-bottom: 18px;
width: fit-content;
}
.alert-dot {
width: 6px; height: 6px;
border-radius: 50%;
background: #e8920a;
box-shadow: 0 0 6px #e8920a;
}
.alert-text {
font-family: ‘Oswald’, sans-serif;
font-size: 11px;
font-weight: 600;
letter-spacing: 4px;
color: #e8920a;
text-transform: uppercase;
}

.title { line-height: 0.88; margin-bottom: 18px; }
.title .based {
display: block;
font-family: ‘Rubik Dirt’, cursive;
font-size: 96px;
color: #f0ede4;
letter-spacing: 2px;
text-transform: uppercase;
}
.title .trenches {
display: block;
font-family: ‘Rubik Dirt’, cursive;
font-size: 96px;
color: #e8920a;
letter-spacing: 2px;
text-transform: uppercase;
text-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(232,146,10,0.2);
}

.hook {
font-family: ‘Oswald’, sans-serif;
font-size: 17px;
font-weight: 400;
color: rgba(230,220,195,0.6);
letter-spacing: 1px;
line-height: 1.5;
margin-bottom: 28px;
}
.hook strong {
color: rgba(230,220,195,0.9);
font-weight: 600;
}

.cta-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 24px; }
.btn-main {
font-family: ‘Oswald’, sans-serif;
font-weight: 700;
font-size: 13px;
letter-spacing: 3px;
text-transform: uppercase;
background: #e8920a;
color: #080806;
padding: 12px 28px;
}
.btn-ghost {
font-family: ‘Oswald’, sans-serif;
font-weight: 600;
font-size: 13px;
letter-spacing: 3px;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: rgba(230,220,195,0.5);
border: 1px solid rgba(230,220,195,0.15);
padding: 11px 24px;
}

.base-badge { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; }
.base-circle { width: 16px; height: 16px; border-radius: 50%; background: #0052ff; box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0,82,255,0.45); flex-shrink: 0; }
.base-text {
font-family: ‘Oswald’, sans-serif;
font-size: 11px;
font-weight: 600;
letter-spacing: 4px;
color: rgba(140,165,255,0.45);
text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* RIGHT - mascot */
.right {
position: relative;
flex: 1;
height: 630px;
overflow: hidden;
z-index: 10;
}

.mascot-img {
position: absolute;
bottom: 0;
right: -20px;
height: 620px;
width: auto;
object-fit: contain;
object-position: bottom right;
}

/* subtle glow behind mascot */
.mascot-glow {
position: absolute;
bottom: -60px;
right: 0;
width: 500px;
height: 500px;
background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(200,146,42,0.06) 0%, transparent 65%);
pointer-events: none;
}

.url-tag {
position: absolute;
bottom: 26px;
left: 64px;
font-family: ‘Oswald’, sans-serif;
font-size: 12px;
letter-spacing: 2px;
color: rgba(200,190,160,0.28);
z-index: 20;
}
</style>

</head>
<body>
<div class="canvas">
  <div class="bg-glow"></div>

  <div class="left">
    <div class="alert-pill">
      <div class="alert-dot"></div>
      <span class="alert-text">Live on Base</span>
    </div>

```
<div class="title">
  <span class="based">Based</span>
  <span class="trenches">Trenches</span>
</div>

<p class="hook">Built by <strong>degens</strong>, for <strong>degens.</strong><br>Fair launches. No rugs. On Base.</p>

<div class="cta-row">
  <div class="btn-main">Launch a Token</div>
  <div class="btn-ghost">Ape In →</div>
</div>

<div class="base-badge">
  <div class="base-circle"></div>
  <span class="base-text">Built on Base</span>
</div>
```

  </div>

  <div class="right">
    <div class="mascot-glow"></div>
    <img class="mascot-img" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="BasedTrenches mascot" />
  </div>

  <div class="url-tag">basedtrenches.fun</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>